'''染料包'''（{{lang-en|'''dye pack'''}}）是一种银行使用{{tsl|en|Radio-control|无线电控制}}的[[燃烧弹|燃烧装置]]，被部分[[銀行|銀行]]用来打击{{tsl|en|Bank robbery|银行劫案}}，在被劫后不久使被盗[[現金|現金]]被[[染料|染料]]永久标记。

在大多数情况下，染料包被放置在[[紙幣|紙幣]]堆（通常是10或20美元）中间的空间中。这样从外观来看就只是一个普通的钞票堆，并且柔性染料包的制造技术也使其难以被检测。<ref name="dyepack">{{Cite web|url=http://science.howstuffworks.com/question671.htm|title=I've heard of bank robbers being foiled by a 'dye pack' put in their money stash. What is a 'dye pack'?|accessdate=May 21, 2012|publisher=How Stuff Works|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224155528/https://science.howstuffworks.com/question671.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

当被标记的钞票堆未使用时，它被存放在银行[[出納員|出納員]]旁边的[[磁|磁性]]板上，处在待机或安全模式，在需要时由银行雇员移交给潜在的强盗。当它被从磁性板上拿开时，此包进入武装状态，一旦离开建筑物并通过门框，位于门框的[[发送器|无线电发射机]]触发一个定时器（通常至少10秒），之后染料包爆炸并释放<ref name="thievescaught">{{Cite web|url=http://nypost.com/2014/05/23/thieves-caught-after-dye-pack-explodes-in-bank-heist/|title=Thieves caught after dye pack explodes in bank heist|accessdate=October 23, 2016|publisher=New York Post|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126101555/https://nypost.com/2014/05/23/thieves-caught-after-dye-pack-explodes-in-bank-heist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[气溶胶|气溶胶]]（通常是[[分散红9|分散红9]]），有时还包括[[催淚彈|催淚彈]]，以摧毁被盗的钞票，并用明显的污迹标记强盗的身体。引起染料包爆炸和染料释放的化学反应会产生大约{{Convert|200|°C}}的高温，进一步阻止犯罪分子接触染料包、从袋内取出染料包或者{{tsl|en|Getaway vehicle|逃离现场}}{{what}}。<ref name="dyepack">{{Cite web|url=http://science.howstuffworks.com/question671.htm|title=I've heard of bank robbers being foiled by a 'dye pack' put in their money stash. What is a 'dye pack'?|accessdate=May 21, 2012|publisher=How Stuff Works}}</ref>染料包已在美国超过75%的银行中使用。<ref name="dyepack">{{Cite web|url=http://science.howstuffworks.com/question671.htm|title=I've heard of bank robbers being foiled by a 'dye pack' put in their money stash. What is a 'dye pack'?|accessdate=May 21, 2012|publisher=How Stuff Works}}</ref>

